snippet.title: A7Xpg (Windows game 2003)
snippet.description:
A7Xpg is a Japanese neon (vector) graphics game by Kenta Cho.
The main character should collect all the yellow gems and avoid enemy units.
You can use the boost function to increase the speed briefly.
